_get_workarea to get the correct screen rectangle.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D49289", "files": ["layout/xul/nsMenuPopupFrame.cpp", "widget/ScreenManager.cpp", "widget/gtk/nsWindow.cpp", "widget/gtk/nsWindow.h", "widget/moz.build", "widget/nsIWidget.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "23e9fe8a919bf7315734c8450913c803b45deac3", "parents": ["3c4f7aa8c9f6c5103679165d49437c97417d3c16"], "tags": []}, {"author": "David Walsh \u003cdwalsh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1583042 - Change devtools debugger shortcut r=Harald\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D47502", "files": ["devtools/client/definitions.js", "devtools/startup/DevToolsStartup.jsm", "devtools/startup/locales/en-US/key-shortcuts.properties"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7bcfcf9c5a8a24ddcd610e82a493020c56b0200e", "parents": ["23e9fe8a919bf7315734c8450913c803b45deac3"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Florin Strugariu \u003cfstrugariu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1589070 - Raptor desktop cold load tests are reusing the initial profile and so are not cold loads r=perftest-reviewers,rwood\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D49421", "files": ["testing/raptor/raptor/raptor.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3536d8186c68a62c891633a17977c23022fe7cf3", "parents": ["7bcfcf9c5a8a24ddcd610e82a493020c56b0200e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Boris Zbarsky \u003cbzbarsky@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1580381.  Fix document.open tests to align with HTML spec changes.  r=hsivonen\n\nSee https://github.com/whatwg/html/issues/4723\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D45478", "files": ["dom/base/Document.cpp", "testing/web-platform/meta/html/webappapis/dynamic-markup-insertion/opening-the-input-stream/aborted-parser.window.js.ini", "testing/web-platform/tests/html/webappapis/dynam