nDrive-by fixes:\n- Remove the unused \"methodName\" argument from `getRelativeTimeFormatInternals`.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D40436", "files": ["js/src/builtin/intl/CommonFunctions.js", "js/src/builtin/intl/RelativeTimeFormat.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b818a65ca8da9bcc6ee5f821a1ae2f1d10e4c52b", "parents": ["448734fab30e8dc1fcc2734c76d6a0339f6de26a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andr\u00e9 Bargull \u003candre.bargull@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1433306 - Part 2: Implement Intl.ListFormat stage 3 proposal. r=jwalden\n\n\"disjunction\" and \"unit\" types aren't yet supported, because ICU doesn't\nprovide a C-API for this functionality. \"short\" and \"narrow\" styles aren't\nsupported for the same reason.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D40437", "files": ["config/check_spidermonkey_style.py", "config/system-headers.mozbuild", "js/public/ProtoKey.h", "js/src/builtin/intl/CommonFunctions.js", "js/src/builtin/intl/IntlObject.cpp", "js/src/builtin/intl/ListFormat.cpp", "js/src/builtin/intl/ListFormat.h", "js/src/builtin/intl/ListFormat.js", "js/src/builtin/intl/SharedIntlData.cpp", "js/src/builtin/intl/SharedIntlData.h", "js/src/jit/InlinableNatives.h", "js/src/jit/MCallOptimize.cpp", "js/src/jsfriendapi.h", "js/src/moz.build", "js/src/shell/js.cpp", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/browser.js", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/conjunction-long.js", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/conjunction-type.js", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/cross-compartment.js", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/disjunction-type.js", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/same-compartment.js", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/shell.js", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/supported-locales.js", "js/src/tests/non262/Intl/ListFormat/unit-type.js", "js/src/vm/CommonPropertyNames.h", "js/src/vm/GlobalObject.cpp", "js/src/vm/SelfHosting.cpp"], "git_no