\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D52671", "files": ["devtools/client/themes/tooltips.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "215108f032e1f8d8dbe52966f173d7678b41f1ba", "parents": ["b17aec293ef449f6043aacb002ff2c6319431f36"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Julian Descottes \u003cjdescottes@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1590408 - Add test to check doorhanger tooltip display on screen edge r=miker a=pascalc\n\nDepends on D52668\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D52647", "files": ["devtools/client/shared/test/browser.ini", "devtools/client/shared/test/browser_html_tooltip_screen_edge.js", "devtools/client/shared/test/browser_html_tooltip_xul-wrapper.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1c5606f276832e74e3ff8d8397708abc4e8c6fb6", "parents": ["215108f032e1f8d8dbe52966f173d7678b41f1ba"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Julian Descottes \u003cjdescottes@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1590408 - Backed out changeset 84708a4f040d from Bug 1552146 r=miker a=pascalc\n\nThe positioning of the arrow was correct, but due to the way the arrow was rotated, the visual center of the arrow did not match the center of the arrow box\nBacking out the JS change here, CSS patch later in the queue\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D52668", "files": ["devtools/client/shared/test/browser_html_tooltip_doorhanger-02.js", "devtools/client/shared/test/browser_html_tooltip_offset.js", "devtools/client/shared/test/browser_html_tooltip_rtl.js", "devtools/client/shared/test/head.js", "devtools/client/shared/test/helper_html_tooltip.js", "devtools/client/shared/widgets/tooltip/HTMLTooltip.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c1279a943d793e2816bf1af10f1bea4f40cb35ca", "parents": ["1c5606f276832e74e3ff8d8397708abc4e8c6fb6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Luca Greco \u003clgreco@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1575891 - browsingData API should not clear nextGen localStorage data stored by browser components and extensions. r=mixedpuppy,asuth,johannh a=pascalc\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D48535", "files": ["browser/components/extensions/parent/ext-browsingData.js", "browser/components/extensions/test/browser/browser_ext_browsingData_localStorage.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b6846fa525a2dd976e16339215c3d63c8fe67245", "parents": ["c1279a943d793e2816bf1af10f1bea4f40cb35ca"], "tags": []}], "date": 1573660004, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "nbeleuzu@mozilla.com"}, "12299": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jan Odvarko \u003codvarko@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1592692 - Enable Resource blocking in all channels r=Harald a=pascalc\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D52335", "files": ["browser/app/profile/firefox.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0b52267741be9490789c279a9cb18a52fef787c0", "parents": ["b6846fa525a2dd976e16339215c3d63c8fe67245"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jim Porter \u003cjporter@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1592470 - Don't cancel content JS when \"navigating\" to javascript: URLs; r=smaug a=pascalc\n\nPrior to this patch, users entering javascript: URLs in the location bar\n(e.g. via a bookmark) would trigger the cancel content JS path for the page\nthey were on, potentially breaking the site. Since javascript: URLs\n(generally) don't navigate to a new page, we should avoid canceling the\ncurrent page's JS.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D51951", "files": ["dom/ipc/BrowserChild.cpp", "dom/ipc/tests/browser_cancel_content_js.js", "dom/ipc/tests/file_cancel_content_js.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "93ae6a5db1d342f4faa1ffe5147b7d0317f9f01b", "parents": ["0b52267741be9490789c279a