3e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1573647, try to make test_windowedhistoryframes.html less racy by using popstate event and not timeout, r=peterv, a=test-only\n\nUsing popstate event in cases it is fired.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D52600", "files": ["dom/tests/mochitest/general/historyframes.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "960b8b72b180d9168a125fdbd63d595e0ba7c45e", "parents": ["fc56c00c1396c979bbd76a86acc6c9795482a6ad"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Neil Deakin \u003cneil@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1444287, wait for the right page to load before performing the test, otherwise about:blank sometimes gets used, r=Gijs, a=test-only\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D52940", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/general/browser_documentnavigation.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6e286b87645c44a174bb5ca35e2632f8e1f086fc", "parents": ["960b8b72b180d9168a125fdbd63d595e0ba7c45e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Neil Deakin \u003cneil@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1580961, disable intermittently failing part of the pointerlock test, leaving the main part that tests the original bug fix, as is, r=Gijs, a=test-only\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D51619", "files": ["dom/tests/browser/browser_pointerlock_warning.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a2195a21717064e8d94d96f2c691a464594da855", "parents": ["6e286b87645c44a174bb5ca35e2632f8e1f086fc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Junior Hsu \u003cjuhsu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576153 - extend timeout to tolerate longer latency from socket layer, r=annevk, a=test-only\n\nExtend timeout to ease intermittent at this moment. File Bug 1595848 for follow-up\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D52714", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/html/cross-origin-embedder-policy/require-corp.https.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "63705cebec52b6e903412511574168353b71dd28", "parents": ["a2195a21717064e8d94d96f2c691a464594da855"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Junior Hsu \u003cjuhsu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1586944 - more reliable way to detect pageLoaded, r=annevk, a=test-only\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D52891", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/html/cross-origin-embedder-policy/none.https.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/html/cross-origin-embedder-policy/require-corp.https.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d6902423f3b5609155bb8bb3e97c49e6898a29e5", "parents": ["63705cebec52b6e903412511574168353b71dd28"], "tags": []}, {"author": "David Parks \u003cdaparks@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1449736: Properly detect failure in receiving plugin NPObjects. r=jmathies, a=pascalc\n\nProperly handles NPError reporting and makes sure that, in the case of failure, it does not return junk for the NPObject.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D48474", "files": ["dom/plugins/ipc/PluginInstanceChild.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5c921325dd03885c3392512722c7cede4ed9e00e", "parents": ["d6902423f3b5609155bb8bb3e97c49e6898a29e5"], "tags": ["DEVEDITION_71_0b11_BUILD1", "DEVEDITION_71_0b11_RELEASE", "FIREFOX_71_0b11_BUILD1", "FIREFOX_71_0b11_RELEASE"]}], "date": 1574091700, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "12323": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\ncy -\u003e 129ceec31f23\nhsb -\u003e 5f158165f5c1\nja -\u003e 639e80dfc1d4\nuk -\u003e d05f1dfd950c", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "no